// LAUNCH OPTIONS

strangle 250 %command% GLX_EXT_swap_control_tear=0 %command% tearfree=0 %command% EnablePageFlip=0 %command% AMD_DEBUG=nir %command% SwapBuffersWait=0 %command% vblank_mode=0 %command% -high -nojoy -noaa -noaafonts -freq 1000 -novid -cl_forcepreload 1 -sv_forcepreload 1 -language bananagaming -tickrate 128 +clientport 27005


// if more than one computer is running steam on your local network, set the "+clientport 27005" option to anything
// between and including 27005 and 27032, excluding 27020 and any number in use on another local machine (27005 is default)
//
// https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?ref=6370-QPHJ-3567
//
//
// "-language bananagaming" enables that text color mod, additional files are needed
//
// NOTE: the %command% environment options may prevent launch with some hardware, nvidia GPUs seem to disagree with them
//
// "strangle ### %command%" sets an external FPS-limiter for Linux, I'm still only testing it for now
//
// "__GL_THREADED_OPTIMIZATIONS=1 %command%" seems to hurt performance about 5% on my R9 390 + AMDGPU while CPU-bound
//
// Linux-focused optimisation guide:
//
// https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1502890492
